
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>My Simple Blog</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #222;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .blog-post {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .blog-post h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .date {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #222;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>My Blog</h1>
    <p>Sharing thoughts, one post at a time</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <div class="blog-post">
        <h2>My First Blog Post</h2>
        <p class="date">March 11, 2026</p>
        <p>
            This is my first blog post. I am learning HTML and this is a simple
            example of how blog content can be displayed using basic tags.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-post">
        <h2>Why I Started Blogging</h2>
        <p class="date">March 10, 2026</p>
        <p>
            Blogging helps me organize my thoughts and share knowledge with others.
            It's simple, effective, and fun to build with HTML.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-post">
        <h2>Learning Web Development</h2>
        <p class="date">March 9, 2026</p>
        <p>
            Web development starts with HTML. Once the structure is ready,
            CSS adds style and JavaScript brings it to life.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 My Blog</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
